  <text class="ui cardTitle" x="72" y="816">Why This Layout</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="72" y="842">1. Explorer stays visible.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="72" y="862">2. Run selected is one click.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="72" y="882">3. Compare is always side-by-side.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="72" y="902">4. Trace and raw IO are local tabs,</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="88" y="918">not global navigation.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="72" y="946">5. The app is about saving LLM tokens,</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="88" y="962">so deltas are first-class columns.</text>

