  <text class="ui cardTitle" x="374" y="522">List Design Notes</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="374" y="548">- The table is the dominant view because the user needs selection, ranking, and bulk runs.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="374" y="568">- Token deltas are first-class columns; they are not hidden inside a detail pane.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="374" y="588">- Compact and hybrid are always visible next to classic, so tradeoffs are immediate.</text>
  <text class="ui small" x="374" y="608">- Status badges call out regressions without opening the testcase.</text>

